name.jp: ジャックザハンマーの売り子
name.vi: Cửa hàng đại lý Jack The Hammer

description.en: This burly Jack The Hammer manages a Personal Shop for you! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.ar: This burly Jack The Hammer manages a Personal Shop for you! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.br: Este forte Jack, o Martelo gerência uma Loja Pessoal para você! Clique duas vezes para fechar a Loja. Você recebe o item de volta quando a loja é fechada.
description.cns: 这个铁锤杰克为您管理个人商店！ 双击关闭商店。 商店关闭后，您可以取回物品。
description.de: Dieser kräftige Jack The Hammer verwaltet deinen persönlichen Shop für dich. Doppelklicke um deinen Shop zu schließen. Du bekommst deine Gegenstände zurück, wenn du den Shop schließt.
description.fi: This burly Jack The Hammer manages a Personal Shop for you! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.fil: This burly Jack The Hammer manages a Personal Shop for you! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.fr: Ce Jackhammer costaud gèrera votre Boutique Personnelle ! Double-cliquez pour fermer la boutique. Vos objets vous seront rendus.
description.id: Jack The Hammer yang kekar ini mengelola Personal Shop untuk Anda! Klik dua kali untuk menutup Shop. Anda mendapatkan barang kembali saat Shop tutup.
description.it: This burly Jack The Hammer manages a Personal Shop for you! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.jp: このジャックザハンマーは、あなたの代わりに個人商店を開いてくれます。使用後はダブルクリックでショップを閉じることができ、アイテムが戻ってきます。
description.kr: 당신을 위해 개인 상점을 관리하는 건장한 잭더해머! 상점을 닫으려면 두 번 클릭하세요. 상점이 닫히면 아이템을 돌려받습니다.
description.nl: This burly Jack The Hammer manages a Personal Shop for you! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.pl: This burly Jack The Hammer manages a Personal Shop for you! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.ru: This burly Jack The Hammer manages a Personal Shop for you! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.sp: ¡Este fornido Jack The Hammer administra una Tienda Personal para ti! Haz doble clic para cerrar la Tienda. Recuperarás el objeto cuando se cierre la tienda.
description.sw: This burly Jack The Hammer manages a Personal Shop for you! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.th: Jack The Hammer ผู้แข็งแกร่งคนนี้จัดการร้านค้าส่วนตัวให้คุณ! ดับเบิ้ลคลิกเพื่อปิดร้าน ได้ของคืนเมื่อร้านปิด
description.tw: 魁武的傑克槌為你管理個人商店，雙擊可以關閉商店，當商店關閉時物品將會返回
description.vi: Jack The Hammer vạm vỡ quản lý một Cửa hàng cá nhân cho bạn! Nhấp đúp để đóng Cửa hàng. Bạn nhận lại hàng khi Shop đóng cửa.
